  <brief_title>Evaluating the Influence of Apnea on Cardiac Function Using Cardiac Magnetic Resonance Imaging.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluating the Influence of Apnea on Heart Function With Strain Analysis and Measurement of Fibrosis Derived From T1-mapping Using Cardiac Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI).</official_title>
  <sponsors>
